<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{{.FestivalName}} - Billet</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0087ff 0%, #4b7ff0 24%, #ce6ed6 48%, #ffc933 78%, #ffe9c7 100%);
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      color: #220850;
    }

    .page {
      width: 920px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .ticket-shell {
      background: #fff7ef;
      border-radius: 28px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(30, 8, 69, 0.18);
      border: 1px solid rgba(123, 63, 168, 0.12);
    }

    .banner-wrap {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1E0845 0%, #7B3FA8 55%, #CE6ED6 100%);
      line-height: 0;
    }

    .banner {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 28px 30px;
      color: #fff5ec;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1E0845 0%, #7B3FA8 55%, #CE6ED6 100%);
    }

    .logo {
      max-height: 56px;
      max-width: 220px;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .festival-name {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      font-size: 44px;
      line-height: .95;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .festival-date {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.92);
    }

    .body {
      padding: 30px;
    }

    .ticket-card {
      display: table;
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 24px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(30,8,69,.10);
      border: 1px solid rgba(123,63,168,.12);
    }

    .main-col,
    .stub-col {
      display: table-cell;
      vertical-align: top;
    }

    .main-col {
      width: 64%;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1E0845 0%, #7B3FA8 55%, #CE6ED6 100%);
      color: #fff5ec;
      padding: 26px 26px 24px;
    }

    .stub-col {
      width: 36%;
      background: #fffdfa;
      border-left: 2px dashed rgba(123,63,168,.22);
      padding: 24px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .pill {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 7px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #fff;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.16);
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .ticket-type {
      margin: 0 0 18px 0;
      font-size: 32px;
      line-height: 1;
      font-weight: 900;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .meta-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    .meta-table td {
      padding: 8px 0;
      vertical-align: top;
    }

    .meta-label {
      width: 130px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 1.6px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.58);
    }

    .meta-value {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff5ec;
    }

    .main-footer {
      margin-top: 22px;
      padding-top: 14px;
      border-top: 1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,.20);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.72);
    }

    .stub-title {
      margin: 0 0 12px 0;
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 1.1;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #220850;
    }

    .qr-box {
      width: 210px;
      height: 210px;
      margin: 0 auto 12px auto;
      padding: 12px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FBF7FF, #FFF5EC);
      border: 1px solid rgba(123,63,168,.14);
      border-radius: 18px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .qr-box img {
      max-width: 100%;
      max-height: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    .ticket-number {
      margin: 8px 0 16px 0;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.3;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #220850;
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    .access-box {
      text-align: left;
      margin-top: 14px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(249,127,160,.08), rgba(255,201,51,.14));
      border: 1px solid rgba(249,127,160,.12);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 14px 14px 12px;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      color: #422917;
    }

    .access-box ul {
      margin: 8px 0 0 18px;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .notice {
      margin-top: 20px;
      background: #fff7f1;
      border: 1px solid #f0c68d;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 15px 16px;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #422917;
    }

    .footer {
      padding: 20px 28px 26px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #7b6d95;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(123,63,168,.10);
      background: #fffdfa;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <div class="ticket-shell">

      <div class="banner-wrap">
        <img src="/top_ticket.svg" alt="Bannière billet" class="banner" />
      </div>

      <div class="hero">
        {{if .LogoURL}}
        <img src="{{.LogoURL}}" alt="Logo {{.FestivalName}}" class="logo" />
        {{end}}
        <h1 class="festival-name">{{.FestivalName}}</h1>
        <p class="festival-date">{{.FestivalDate}}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="body">
        <div class="ticket-card">
          <div class="main-col">
            <div class="pill">Billet festival</div>
            <h2 class="ticket-type">{{.TicketTypeName}}</h2>

            <table class="meta-table">
              <tr>
                <td class="meta-label">Client</td>
                <td class="meta-value">{{.CustomerName}}</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="meta-label">Commande</td>
                <td class="meta-value">{{.OrderNumber}}</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="meta-label">Participant</td>
                <td class="meta-value">{{if .AttendeeName}}{{.AttendeeName}}{{else}}{{.CustomerName}}{{end}}</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="meta-label">Date</td>
                <td class="meta-value">{{.FestivalDate}}</td>
              </tr>
            </table>

            <div class="main-footer">
              Ce billet est personnel et ne peut être validé qu’une seule fois. Présentez votre QR code à l’entrée du festival. Pour toute question : {{.SupportEmail}}
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="stub-col">
            <h3 class="stub-title">QR code billet</h3>

            <div class="qr-box">
              <img src="{{.QRCodeDataURI}}" alt="QR code billet">
            </div>

            <div class="ticket-number">{{.QRToken}}</div>

            <div class="access-box">
              <strong>Conditions d’accès</strong>
              <ul>
                <li>Présenter son billet</li>
                <li>Pièce d’identité possible à l’entrée</li>
                <li>Respect et bienveillance</li>
              </ul>
              <div style="margin-top:10px;">L’événement est filmé et photographié.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="notice">
          <strong>La revente de ce billet n’est pas autorisée.</strong><br>
          Toute tentative de revente ou d’utilisation frauduleuse peut entraîner son invalidation.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        {{.FestivalName}} — {{.FestivalDate}} — Contact : {{.SupportEmail}}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>